WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.467 --> 00:00:03.742
We're so thankful for his presence already here.

00:00:03.742 --> 00:00:15.534
I feel him, I feel the glory in the house, and I'm so grateful for every single one of you that have come out tonight to pray with us.

00:00:24.378 --> 00:00:31.255
In just a couple of minutes, we already have almost 1,500 people here, and I'm just so grateful for every single one of you that come out and take prayer seriously.

00:00:31.255 --> 00:00:42.944
We have a lot of work to do, so we'll get right to it.

00:00:45.007 --> 00:01:02.333
I want to go over some of the things that the Lord showed us over the last prayer time we had.

00:01:02.333 --> 00:01:29.474
Over the last couple of videos, some of the things that we have seen by the leading of the Holy Spirit are in the news now.

00:01:29.474 --> 00:02:06.873
I want to give all glory and honor to Jesus that I have a treasure in an earthen vessel, that the excellency of the power is known of him and not of me.

00:02:06.873 --> 00:02:33.360
I want to tell you all immediately, everything that we see, everything we do, we give all to the glory of God.

00:02:33.360 --> 00:02:46.114
It's all his glory—none of me and all of him.

00:02:56.033 --> 00:03:02.644
And so I'm excited when we see what we've been praying for, and it's in the news today.

00:03:22.475 --> 00:03:23.136
I said, 'We don't pray the news; we pray for what's coming in the news.

00:03:23.136 --> 00:03:35.696
' We are the news, and people will come here to get the news first.

00:03:35.696 --> 00:03:45.269
I believe in being prophetic and accurate and not being flaky in these last days.

00:03:45.269 --> 00:03:50.580
If I miss it, I'll be the first one to tell you; I'm just human.

00:03:51.698 --> 00:03:55.332
We all have missed it and we all try our best to be accurate.

00:03:55.891 --> 00:03:56.730
But you know what?

00:03:56.730 --> 00:03:57.568
We're flesh.

00:03:58.687 --> 00:04:06.604
That pipe sometimes gets a little cocky, and we have to make sure that we keep our thermostat right so that we don't lead people astray.

00:04:06.604 --> 00:04:09.070
My heart is always to do right.

00:04:11.263 --> 00:04:17.840
I want to tell you thank you for being here, and thank you for trusting us to pray with us and to do things we're doing.

00:04:27.802 --> 00:04:28.110
It's all Jesus.

00:04:31.806 --> 00:04:32.115
So, let's go over some of the news real quick.

00:04:32.115 --> 00:04:35.503
We'll talk about it and see what we found.

00:04:35.503 --> 00:04:40.883
Braden said, 'Dad, did you see what happened today in the news concerning NASA?

00:04:40.883 --> 00:04:41.813
' NASA?

00:04:41.813 --> 00:04:43.363
How many of y'all?

00:04:43.363 --> 00:04:48.013
Go ahead and play the clip of what the Lord showed us.

00:04:48.013 --> 00:04:50.183
Do you have that ready?

00:04:50.183 --> 00:04:50.803
Yes.

00:04:51.733 --> 00:04:57.313
I want you just to play some of the things the Lord showed us about the moon.

00:04:57.313 --> 00:04:58.243
Excuse me.

00:04:58.243 --> 00:05:01.724
This was on December the 2nd of last year.

00:05:01.724 --> 00:05:02.510
Go ahead.

00:05:02.510 --> 00:05:06.180
'I hear them say they're going to go to the moon.

00:05:06.180 --> 00:05:08.539
They want to go to the moon.

00:05:08.539 --> 00:05:10.635
There's a base on the moon.

00:05:12.732 --> 00:05:12.994
I kid you not.

00:05:12.994 --> 00:05:14.305
I see a structure.

00:05:14.305 --> 00:05:15.615
I see a structure.

00:05:15.615 --> 00:05:17.450
How is that even possible?

00:05:17.450 --> 00:05:18.760
Is that it, Lord?

00:05:28.138 --> 00:05:28.510
What am I seeing on this space race?

00:05:28.510 --> 00:05:29.625
Space race?

00:05:42.767 --> 00:05:43.311
Yes.

00:05:43.311 --> 00:05:44.945
Space race.

00:05:44.945 --> 00:05:55.117
' Okay, so in the space race, I saw a thing on the moon's surface.

00:05:55.117 --> 00:05:59.610
It looked like a dome with lights on it.

00:05:59.610 --> 00:06:09.821
Now, I don't know what I was looking at, but it looked like box windows of some kind of light.

00:06:09.821 --> 00:06:24.605
They had made some kind of base—trying to make a base to escape the earth, to get away from all the drama going down here and go to the moon.

00:06:28.734 --> 00:06:29.109
I saw a base that looked like pods.

00:06:33.238 --> 00:06:37.368
They looked like little places, but people were trying to fly up there to stay on the moon.

00:06:37.368 --> 00:06:40.371
I was like, 'What is this?

00:06:40.371 --> 00:06:43.374
' So, a new space race.

00:06:50.230 --> 00:07:03.267
And I saw—which, if it was legitimate the first time, I don't understand why this would be such a big deal the second time—but it was a space race to get to the moon again with actual astronauts landing on the moon.

00:07:03.717 --> 00:07:06.787
I saw actual stuff happening with that.

00:07:07.555 --> 00:07:08.323
A real something.

00:07:09.474 --> 00:07:13.312
I thought that was interesting because these spaceships were different.

00:07:13.312 --> 00:07:20.221
I was like, 'What is going on with this?

00:07:20.221 --> 00:07:25.979
' In the vision, I could see that it was so clear.

00:07:29.923 --> 00:07:30.346
I saw the space race.

00:07:30.346 --> 00:07:43.038
Next, I see technological advancements, and it will be shock and awe and the uncovering of the technological advancements that the United States possesses.

00:08:03.867 --> 00:08:09.366
Some will say it looks like alien technology.

00:08:10.741 --> 00:08:19.677
Even in the days ahead, there will be even greater things because of quantum computing.

00:08:19.677 --> 00:08:29.300
There's a breakthrough concerning fuel—a breakthrough for a fuel with water.

00:08:29.400 --> 00:08:35.283
The splitting of what you would consider an atom.

00:08:35.283 --> 00:08:45.087
Endless energy, I hear the Lord say, is coming—greater than petrol.

00:08:45.087 --> 00:08:47.048
The blue light.

00:08:47.048 --> 00:09:02.736
It's by mathematical equations that they're going to achieve this new energy that is greater than the splitting of an atom, like nuclear.

00:09:28.723 --> 00:09:29.250
It's greater than nuclear.

00:09:37.682 --> 00:09:38.209
And it will be in jets—clean energy.

00:09:39.789 --> 00:09:48.575
I hear clean energy better than fossil fuels is coming with the splitting of new energy.

00:10:01.996 --> 00:10:05.575
They're about to harness it.

00:10:05.575 --> 00:10:11.838
They're about to harness this new blue energy.

00:10:16.312 --> 00:10:18.101
And when it does, it spins with bubbles with great electricity.

00:10:50.565 --> 00:10:50.916
It looks like pulses.

00:10:53.380 --> 00:10:54.084
That is blue light and it's split.

00:10:54.084 --> 00:10:57.956
I see the bubbles in it in a laboratory with water all around it.

00:10:58.308 --> 00:11:02.883
The mathematical equation is even greater than what they've had before.

00:11:06.754 --> 00:11:08.162
You know, they say hydrogen fusion, this hydrogen molecule, a hydrogen engine.

00:11:08.162 --> 00:11:10.956
It is something greater for jets.

00:11:10.956 --> 00:11:15.239
And they're trying to say, 'Well, we'll use it for...

00:11:15.239 --> 00:11:20.511
' I hear it's Elon for going to Mars for long, sustainable energy.

00:11:20.511 --> 00:11:29.078
Remember I told you a new space race is coming, and I said don't try to do things on the moon.

00:11:32.337 --> 00:11:36.365
And it's going to be like I saw—and I told you, I saw the base.

00:11:38.782 --> 00:11:47.241
It was in the picture, and I saw they're going to try to do things on the moon with this new technology.

00:11:57.715 --> 00:11:58.118
It's a blue energy and it's better than nuclear.

00:11:58.118 --> 00:11:58.923
Okay.

00:11:58.923 --> 00:12:02.185
So then we hear what happened today.

00:12:02.185 --> 00:12:04.686
Do you have the video?

00:12:04.686 --> 00:12:05.401
Yeah.

00:12:05.401 --> 00:12:07.188
Go ahead and play.

00:12:07.188 --> 00:12:15.764
'We're going to hit pause on the gateway, which was a space station designed to orbit above the moon.

00:12:15.764 --> 00:12:16.479
Right.

00:12:30.354 --> 00:12:30.651
You don't want to orbit above the moon.

00:12:30.651 --> 00:12:33.321
We want to be on the moon.

00:12:33.321 --> 00:12:35.695
We want to build the base.

00:12:35.695 --> 00:12:38.365
We want to interact with the regolith.

00:12:38.365 --> 00:12:41.036
We want to do in-situ resource manufacturing.

00:12:41.036 --> 00:12:46.445
We want to test out mobility on the surface to power communications.

00:12:46.445 --> 00:12:54.236
We want to build President Trump's moon base that he called for in the national space policy.

00:12:54.236 --> 00:12:57.576
We have the resources to do this.

00:12:57.576 --> 00:13:01.286
We have a lot of resources at NASA.

00:13:01.286 --> 00:13:06.109
We just need to move them in the needle-moving direction.

00:13:06.109 --> 00:13:09.203
' So they admitted it today.

00:13:09.203 --> 00:13:10.714
Isn't that amazing?

00:13:23.175 --> 00:13:23.553
The things we see in the spirit, they're talking about doing them now.

00:13:25.441 --> 00:13:26.196
And today they announced it.

00:13:26.196 --> 00:13:29.594
'We want to build a moon base.

00:13:29.594 --> 00:13:32.993
We want to do all these things.

00:13:32.993 --> 00:13:39.821
We don't want to just orbit the moon; we want to build something on the moon.

00:13:39.821 --> 00:13:43.577
' And I said they're going to do it.

00:13:43.577 --> 00:13:44.942
I've seen it.

00:13:57.885 --> 00:14:02.308
I know how they do it.

00:14:03.783 --> 00:14:04.667
I watched how they do it.

00:14:12.924 --> 00:14:14.693
And so there's more clips here.

00:14:14.759 --> 00:14:20.502
'First, in the future, we will build the moon base in three phases.

00:14:20.502 --> 00:14:29.835
Phase one endeavors to support industry by moving from infrequent, bespoke efforts to a templated approach that will generate significant learning.

00:14:29.835 --> 00:14:53.254
Through experimentation, we will dramatically expand lunar landings through the CLPS and the LTV program, delivering rovers, instruments, and technology payloads that test mobility and power systems, such as working with international partners and industry on the production of RTGs and RHUs, communications, navigation, surface operations, and all the science payload that can be incorporated.

00:14:53.254 --> 00:15:02.215
Phase two transitions from experimentation to semi-habitable infrastructure and routine logistics, with the aim of supporting regular astronaut operations on the surface.

00:15:02.215 --> 00:15:09.797
It's at this point we anticipate seeing the significant contributions from our great partners like JAXA's pressurized rover.

00:15:09.797 --> 00:15:26.167
Phase three takes advantage of the affordable mass-to-surface capabilities that cargo HLS will inevitably provide in the years ahead and enables the permanent infrastructure necessary to sustain a human presence, such as Italy's proposed habitation module.

00:15:31.413 --> 00:15:31.797
The moon base will not appear overnight.

00:15:42.950 --> 00:15:46.411
We will invest approximately $20 billion over the next seven years and build it through dozens of missions, working together with commercial and international partners towards a deliberate and achievable plan.

00:15:46.411 --> 00:16:12.284
Just as there was Mercury and Gemini before Apollo, there will be an evolutionary path to building humanity's first permanent surface outpost beyond Earth, and we will take the world along with us as they follow along on the NASA moon base website and watch the assembly through lunar relay and observation satellites.

00:16:12.284 --> 00:16:21.226
' When the Lord tells us before the world gets to hear it, it's all to his glory.

00:16:21.293 --> 00:16:22.611
Isn't that neat?

00:16:24.259 --> 00:16:32.496
I said, 'Lord, you're talking to us, and we're hearing it over the course of the last eight or nine months or a year.

00:16:32.496 --> 00:16:36.780
' And it's accurate, what the Lord is showing us.

00:16:44.764 --> 00:16:45.131
And you say, 'Well, Brandon, that's kind of scary.

00:16:45.131 --> 00:16:46.600
Why are they doing all that?

00:16:46.600 --> 00:16:48.803
' Because the end is coming.

00:16:55.412 --> 00:16:55.779
You all have to understand.

00:16:55.779 --> 00:16:57.248
They see something.

00:17:10.991 --> 00:17:13.601
I told you I saw an asteroid coming.

00:17:18.448 --> 00:17:18.821
I saw them in meetings.

00:17:19.940 --> 00:17:22.922
The Lord allowed me to go to these meetings.

00:17:35.715 --> 00:17:36.104
I hear what they're saying.

00:17:36.104 --> 00:17:39.993
There is an object that is approaching Earth.

00:17:43.493 --> 00:17:45.437
And the Lord showed me mathematical equations all on this table.

00:17:58.270 --> 00:17:58.659
And he said their mathematical equations are wrong; it will hit Earth.

00:17:58.659 --> 00:18:00.569
It's in my word.

00:18:00.569 --> 00:18:03.171
It will not be avoided.

00:18:03.171 --> 00:18:12.090
But this object that they know is coming, they're trying to prepare, saying, 'The odds are in our favor.

00:18:13.576 --> 00:18:15.062
The odds are in our favor.

00:18:15.062 --> 00:18:17.664
It will not touch Earth.

00:18:17.664 --> 00:18:19.150
' They're wrong.

00:18:19.150 --> 00:18:20.265
It will.

00:18:23.610 --> 00:18:25.468
The Lord said this and he said, 'It's in my word.

00:18:25.468 --> 00:18:26.954
It's called Wormwood.

00:18:26.954 --> 00:18:32.872
' And many people do not realize the signs of the times.

00:18:32.872 --> 00:18:38.743
In the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ, it's all around us.

00:18:42.657 --> 00:18:43.048
I try to warn you all the time.

00:18:52.183 --> 00:18:52.445
I said, 'Lord, all the things that we talk about, everything in the accuracy of what we see...

00:18:52.445 --> 00:18:54.541
' We all see in part.

00:19:01.879 --> 00:19:02.141
And I believe that everybody has the ability, if you're a born-again Christian, to hear the voice of God for yourself.

00:19:05.023 --> 00:19:05.285
You don't need us.

00:19:10.264 --> 00:19:10.526
You just need the Holy Spirit, and you already have him.

00:19:10.526 --> 00:19:18.881
If you recognize him and invite him into your house, if you invite him into your temple...

00:19:18.881 --> 00:19:22.462
You know what his address is like?

00:19:27.634 --> 00:19:28.032
You have an address to your home.

00:19:28.032 --> 00:19:30.817
His address is your name.

00:19:32.806 --> 00:19:33.204
It's you.

00:19:33.204 --> 00:19:35.193
His address is you.

00:19:50.136 --> 00:19:50.454
He dwells on the inside of you, and most people don't even give him the time of day to even say, 'Welcome, Holy Spirit.

00:19:50.454 --> 00:19:52.043
How are you doing?

00:19:52.043 --> 00:19:53.313
How's your day?

00:19:53.313 --> 00:19:54.584
Let's be friends.

00:19:54.584 --> 00:19:55.855
Let's talk things.

00:19:55.855 --> 00:19:58.078
Show me the secret things.

00:19:58.078 --> 00:20:01.573
Show me the mysteries that no one else knows.

00:20:01.573 --> 00:20:10.728
' And if you treat him like a friend and not like some far-out religious object, he is an ever-present help in a time of need.

00:20:10.728 --> 00:20:16.101
But there are so many people that don't allow the Holy Spirit to invade them.

00:20:16.101 --> 00:20:22.034
You should allow him to take you over and say, 'Hey, I yield myself to you.

00:20:22.034 --> 00:20:25.905
I want you to become more real to me.

00:20:25.905 --> 00:20:29.073
I want to be wall-to-wall Holy Ghost.

00:20:29.073 --> 00:20:33.648
' And what people don't realize is he's a gentleman.

00:20:33.648 --> 00:20:37.168
He'll never force his way in on you.

00:20:37.168 --> 00:20:42.799
If he's knocking on your heart, he doesn't just shove the door open.

00:20:44.881 --> 00:20:45.391
He wants you to invite him.

00:20:45.391 --> 00:20:50.742
Day by day, just like I would go to somebody's house, I would knock on their door.

00:20:50.742 --> 00:20:56.094
Even if it was the second day and I was there the night before, you always knock.

00:20:57.878 --> 00:20:58.133
You're a gentleman.

00:21:01.191 --> 00:21:01.446
You don't just barge into their house.

00:21:03.485 --> 00:21:04.759
You knock and say, 'Hey, I'm here.

00:21:04.759 --> 00:21:07.391
' And that's the way he is.

00:21:07.391 --> 00:21:08.561
'Hey, I'm here.

00:21:08.561 --> 00:21:11.192
Will you allow me to lead you?

00:21:25.721 --> 00:21:31.031
Will you allow me to fill you?

00:21:31.031 --> 00:21:34.466
' Like that guy says, 'Fill my cup, Lord.

00:21:34.466 --> 00:21:37.902
' Why do I sing that song so much?

00:21:37.902 --> 00:21:41.338
'Fill my cup, Lord, I lift it up, Lord.

00:21:41.338 --> 00:21:43.837
' It's because we leak out.

00:21:43.837 --> 00:21:54.205
And the more we leak out, the more we have all this trash around us and the dark's getting darker, the more we have to remain filled.

00:21:54.205 --> 00:21:59.509
It's like my friend Billy Burke says, 'You let your full fight for you.

00:21:59.509 --> 00:22:02.316
' You have to let your full fight for you.

00:22:02.316 --> 00:22:08.556
If you're empty, you're not going to be able to resist the devil like you should.

00:22:14.238 --> 00:22:14.516
You must be filled and controlled by the Holy Ghost in these last days.

00:22:14.516 --> 00:22:18.418
So I just encourage you even more so to remain full.

00:22:18.418 --> 00:22:23.156
You don't need a YouTube channel to help you in your relationship with God.

00:22:23.156 --> 00:22:31.761
I might encourage you and we pray together, for many hands make light work, but you need to have an intimate relationship with God by yourself and you must find him.

00:22:31.761 --> 00:22:34.218
You're running out of time.

00:22:34.218 --> 00:22:37.026
It's time to stop playing church.

00:22:37.026 --> 00:22:38.781
Jesus Christ is coming.

00:22:38.781 --> 00:22:41.238
He's standing at the door.

00:22:41.238 --> 00:22:45.800
I'm telling you, I've seen vision after vision of him.

00:22:45.800 --> 00:22:48.257
He's coming, ladies and gentlemen.

00:22:48.959 --> 00:22:52.118
This dispensation of grace is coming to an end.

00:22:52.118 --> 00:22:56.767
Everything we know is about to accelerate at an even greater scale.

00:22:56.767 --> 00:23:05.708
As of April 1st, the Lord said, when Passover comes, the birthing pains will now double, even greater than what they were from Rosh Hashanah on the 23rd.

00:23:05.708 --> 00:23:12.779
It was six months, and he said this is another window and another acceleration of things is about to take place.

00:23:12.779 --> 00:23:16.931
But it won't just be with wars and rumors of wars.

00:23:16.931 --> 00:23:21.973
In Matthew 24, it talks about wars, earthquakes in divers places, plagues, and pestilence.

00:23:21.973 --> 00:23:24.642
But these are the beginning of sorrows.

00:23:25.532 --> 00:23:28.498
I want you to see what happened again today.

00:23:28.498 --> 00:23:33.243
I told you, we're about to see major asteroids all throughout the Earth.

00:23:33.243 --> 00:23:41.303
Things are going to be freaking people out because of fearful sights you will see that will bring you to your knees.

00:23:49.375 --> 00:23:49.674
He said, 'Brandon, I'm taking My hand off of certain things to shake the earth because they're asleep.

00:23:49.674 --> 00:24:04.113
They're not awake for what's about to take place, and they must know that this dispensation of grace is coming to an end, for I'm going to give them signs now in the heavens.

00:24:04.113 --> 00:24:09.605
' Remember when I told you that there was none of this?

00:24:09.605 --> 00:24:12.169
Now look what happened today—yesterday.

00:24:12.169 --> 00:24:13.1000
Go ahead, play it.

00:24:13.1000 --> 00:24:15.465
Look at them.

00:24:15.465 --> 00:24:18.760
Okay, well, go ahead and tell him.

00:24:18.760 --> 00:24:19.493
Yeah.

00:24:19.493 --> 00:24:24.129
See this one?

00:24:24.129 --> 00:24:25.682
This is California.

00:24:25.682 --> 00:24:26.846
They're falling.

00:24:44.312 --> 00:24:44.632
I told you, the rocks are coming.

00:24:44.632 --> 00:24:46.228
There's one right there.

00:24:46.228 --> 00:24:47.825
There's one right here.

00:24:47.825 --> 00:24:49.102
Where's this one?

00:24:49.102 --> 00:24:51.976
I think this is the same one.

00:24:51.976 --> 00:24:52.615
Boom!

00:25:00.917 --> 00:25:06.757
I said it will be so loud soon that it will break the glass out of your houses and your cars because it will be such a sonic boom and it will be coming so fast.

00:25:07.753 --> 00:25:10.076
And I said it will shake the buildings.

00:25:10.076 --> 00:25:11.072
That's Ohio.

00:25:11.072 --> 00:25:12.731
Do you see them?

00:25:23.684 --> 00:25:24.016
They're coming.

00:25:25.675 --> 00:25:26.339
And the Lord warned us.

00:25:26.671 --> 00:25:30.928
The second phase is upon us; it starts April 1st.

00:25:30.928 --> 00:25:32.530
It's already happening.

00:25:36.535 --> 00:25:36.936
The birthing pains, He said, will come.

00:25:44.545 --> 00:25:44.946
It will start to be out of what you see.

00:25:46.147 --> 00:25:54.558
You have wars and rumors of wars, and now we'll start to go to the signs of the heavens.

00:25:54.558 --> 00:25:59.551
Five major shakings, He said, will start to take place in the earth.

00:25:59.551 --> 00:26:01.557
What are those major shakings?

00:26:01.557 --> 00:26:03.850
He's going to shake the church.

00:26:17.661 --> 00:26:17.954
He's going to shake the heavens.

00:26:17.954 --> 00:26:22.053
He's going to shake the earth's crust with earthquakes and volcanoes.

00:26:22.053 --> 00:26:26.445
He's going to shake politics, and He's going to shake the finances.

