Father, I thank you, Lord, that it's time for the exceedingly, abundantly above all that we dare ask or think—that it is a time to excel, to be the head and not the tail, above and not beneath, that we are the children of the Most High God.

01:25:39.432 --> 01:25:49.391
We're seated with you in the heavenlies, far above all principalities and powers and might.

01:25:49.391 --> 01:25:57.262
We believe that you've made us joint heirs with you.

01:25:57.262 --> 01:26:06.343
We believe that we'll lay hands on the sick and they'll recover.

01:26:06.343 --> 01:26:13.180
We believe that we can cast out devils in your name.

01:26:13.180 --> 01:26:18.995
We believe we will raise the dead in your name.

01:26:18.995 --> 01:26:29.730
Father, I thank you, Lord, that you have called us to the kingdom for such a time as this.

01:26:29.730 --> 01:26:35.993
Father, I thank you, Lord, that it's all hands on deck.

01:26:43.693 --> 01:26:44.076
You said the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

01:26:44.076 --> 01:26:49.826
Father, I thank you, Lord, that we're calling forth the laborers tonight.

01:26:49.826 --> 01:26:59.918
We're calling forth the people that have a backbone like a crowbar that are ready to take the land for Jesus.

01:27:04.895 --> 01:27:14.020
And we thank you, Father, that we are the overcomers, and we're bringing in the biggest harvest this world has ever seen for such a time as this.

01:27:21.485 --> 01:27:23.144
And we take this body in the name of Jesus, and we thank you, Lord, that we're healed.

01:27:23.144 --> 01:27:25.142
Today is your day.

01:27:25.142 --> 01:27:26.278
Believe it.

01:27:26.278 --> 01:27:31.204
Don't look at this as just a piece of cracker.

01:27:31.204 --> 01:27:35.371
Look at it as: 'I'm healed by his stripes.

01:27:35.371 --> 01:27:41.812
' And as I take this body, he took all the sickness for me.

01:27:41.812 --> 01:27:47.725
And what he bore in his body, I need not bear in mine.

01:27:47.725 --> 01:27:58.654
I believe that Jesus Christ died for me, and he took it all, and I'm healed and whole and well in the mighty name of Jesus.

01:27:58.654 --> 01:28:00.704
And we take it right now in Jesus' name.

01:28:10.304 --> 01:28:10.613
Lord, we make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

01:28:10.613 --> 01:28:14.938
We apply the blood over our eyes and over our ears.

01:28:14.938 --> 01:28:19.263
If anything you want to show us tonight, Father, we're here.

01:28:19.263 --> 01:28:22.662
If not, we'll just pray and give you praise.

01:28:22.662 --> 01:28:37.733
Father, we lift up this time, and I yield to the anointing of the watchman, I yield to the anointing of the prophetic, I yield to the anointing of what you've called me to do.

01:28:37.733 --> 01:28:40.885
Father, we warn the people of what is to come.

01:28:44.825 --> 01:28:47.189
We apply the blood uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

01:28:57.897 --> 01:28:58.252
I thank you, Lord, that I hear you and see what you want me to see.

01:28:58.252 --> 01:29:09.285
And we thank you, Lord, that the blood of Jesus Christ covers us from the top of our head to the soles of our feet.

01:29:09.285 --> 01:29:12.132
Now, station angels all around here.

01:29:12.132 --> 01:29:17.114
And I thank you, Lord, for my angels that protect us.

01:29:17.114 --> 01:29:26.234
And we thank you, Lord, that they bear us up in their hands, lest we dash our foot against a stone.

01:29:43.197 --> 01:29:43.543
And we take the blood right now, in Jesus' name, Amen and amen.

01:29:43.543 --> 01:29:48.671
Let's do that often in remembrance of what he did for us.

01:29:48.671 --> 01:29:52.885
It's not something religious; it's about relationship in a covenant.

01:30:04.879 --> 01:30:05.203
As he is, so are we in this world.

01:30:05.203 --> 01:30:08.121
He dwells on the inside of you.

01:30:25.947 --> 01:30:26.318
I practice his presence.

01:30:26.318 --> 01:30:33.371
He spoke to me first thing this morning and talked to me about my future.

01:30:33.371 --> 01:30:40.795
I love the Lord Jesus, but it's not just some religious experience; it's a personal relationship.

01:30:40.795 --> 01:30:46.362
I don't look at him as some kind of far-off God that I can't talk to.

01:30:59.944 --> 01:31:00.360
He's an ever-present help in a time of need.

01:31:00.360 --> 01:31:07.430
Change your glasses, change the way you see the Lord—that he is your friend.

01:31:07.430 --> 01:31:11.173
He'll change you from the inside out.

01:31:11.173 --> 01:31:16.995
But who can go and approach a God that feels untouchable?

01:31:16.995 --> 01:31:23.205
I always keep my sense of awe and respect of him.

01:31:23.205 --> 01:31:32.098
I'm not looking at it like, 'Let's bump fists and have a glass of coconut milk.

01:31:32.098 --> 01:31:40.990
' I honor him and I reverence him, but I always approach him as a friend.

01:31:40.990 --> 01:31:47.132
He's holy, but he is worthy, and he's my friend.

01:32:15.487 --> 01:32:16.076
I believe in miracles.

01:32:16.076 --> 01:32:20.785
I've seen a soul set free.

01:32:20.785 --> 01:32:26.672
Miraculous the change in one redeemed through Calvary.

01:32:26.672 --> 01:32:35.493
I've seen the lily push its way up through the stubborn sod.

01:32:35.493 --> 01:32:41.801
I believe in miracles, for I believe in God.

01:32:58.432 --> 01:32:59.005
We believe today there's an expiration date for all those that are heavy laden.

01:32:59.579 --> 01:33:04.620
You said you'd give them rest tonight.

01:33:06.543 --> 01:33:18.627
Father, I thank you, Lord, that tonight's the night for their breakthrough in their marriages.

01:33:18.627 --> 01:33:38.833
I thank you that tonight's the night for a breakthrough of being single and feeling so alone, that you're bringing in the perfect spouse to the single, that you're bringing restoration to the marriages that are broken and separated.

01:33:38.833 --> 01:33:47.682
There's really no root cause other than the devil has been after you.

01:33:52.740 --> 01:34:10.142
And so you've become weary in well-doing, and things seem to be overwhelming you.

01:34:10.142 --> 01:34:17.057
Jesus wants to give you hope tonight in what we call a mending of the hearts.

01:34:17.057 --> 01:34:18.785
Faith works by love.

01:34:18.785 --> 01:34:31.577
Father, we thank you, Lord, that love takes no account of a suffered wrong, even as many people try to be rude and do things that are rude to us.

01:34:31.577 --> 01:34:35.380
Father, we take no account of who suffered wrong.

01:34:35.380 --> 01:34:37.327
Love never fails.

01:34:37.327 --> 01:34:45.155
Tonight we thank you that love takes us over, for God is love.

01:34:45.155 --> 01:34:49.069
Let love take us over tonight.

01:34:49.069 --> 01:35:08.581
Father, as we love the nations, as we call for the unsaved to find the saving knowledge of the Lord Jesus Christ, we call for the eyes of their understanding to be enlightened.

01:35:17.484 --> 01:35:17.871
Lord, we call the blinders off.

01:35:17.871 --> 01:35:29.871
For you said Satan has blinded the eyes of the unbeliever, and we call the blinders off of their eyes in the name of Jesus.

01:35:29.871 --> 01:35:40.322
According to Ephesians 1:18, that the eyes of their understanding would be enlightened, that they would see how much Jesus loves them.

01:35:40.322 --> 01:35:48.075
We take authority over the demonic spirits that have been sent to kill, steal, and destroy.

01:35:48.075 --> 01:35:57.393
Father, you said, 'I have come that you might have life and abundance to the full, until it overflows.

01:35:57.393 --> 01:36:14.190
' I believe that tonight is the night of a turnaround for many people who are believing for breakthrough in their finances, in their homes, in their marriages, and for their wayward children.

01:36:14.190 --> 01:36:19.684
We call them home in the name of Jesus.

01:36:20.184 --> 01:36:34.669
The Bible says, 'Train up a child in the way they should go, and when they get older, they will not depart from it.

01:36:34.669 --> 01:36:41.662
' We call those children home in the name of Jesus.

01:36:41.662 --> 01:36:48.814
Even if there's just one seed of hope, we thank you, Lord.

01:36:48.814 --> 01:36:54.645
Some plant, some water, but God brings forth the increase.

01:37:05.858 --> 01:37:06.307
And we thank you, Lord, that you're bringing forth that increase—thirty, sixty, and 100-fold.

01:37:12.138 --> 01:37:16.233
We call it in right now in the name of Jesus from the north, south, east, and west.

01:37:16.233 --> 01:37:20.308
Satan, get your hands off of our finances!

01:37:34.977 --> 01:37:43.126
You will not touch God's property, and I call back what you stole sevenfold in Jesus' name.

01:38:05.376 --> 01:38:05.859
We say we are blessed.

01:38:05.859 --> 01:38:14.057
We're prosperous in the city and in the field, coming in and going out.

01:38:14.057 --> 01:38:16.468
Overflow is the way.

01:38:16.468 --> 01:38:26.712
Our storehouses overflow so that we lack no good thing; the willing and obedient eat the good of the land.

01:38:31.078 --> 01:38:58.614
We thank you, Lord, that tonight's the night we see breakthrough, a turnaround, a divine reversal, and a divine turnaround tonight in the name of Jesus for jobs and better jobs, raises and bonuses, benefits, sales and commission growth, estates and inheritances, rebates and returns, checks in the mail, gifts and surprises, found money, bills paid off, bills decreased, and blessing and increase on our households.

01:38:59.136 --> 01:39:06.622
We believe that it is a time that we're going to excel.

01:39:06.622 --> 01:39:09.528
We're the salty ones.

01:39:09.528 --> 01:39:21.153
People are drawn to the salt and they ask, 'What is it about you that's different?

01:39:21.153 --> 01:39:31.627
' We arise and shine, for the light has come, and the glory of the Lord is risen on us.

01:39:34.615 --> 01:39:39.469
That light shines so bright through our eyes and through us that people see it in Walmart.

01:39:39.469 --> 01:39:42.456
They see it wherever we go.

01:39:42.456 --> 01:39:49.551
We may go down to Cracker Barrel and they say, 'There's something different about you.

01:39:49.551 --> 01:39:52.912
' It's not me; it's all Jesus.

01:39:52.912 --> 01:40:11.628
There's something different about you as you go into the Cracker Barrel, as you go into the IHOP, or wherever you may be, because wherever you go, you take Jesus with you.

01:40:11.628 --> 01:40:16.484
His presence is felt, flooding my whole house.

01:40:29.999 --> 01:40:30.313
The King is here.

01:40:30.313 --> 01:40:31.568
We acknowledge you.

01:40:31.568 --> 01:40:35.960
The King is here.

01:40:35.960 --> 01:40:42.235
Holy, holy, holy is the Lord of hosts, who was and is and is to come.

01:40:42.235 --> 01:40:48.068
Holy, holy, holy is the Lord, who was and is and is to come.

01:40:48.068 --> 01:40:52.068
Fill my cup, Lord; I lift it up, Lord.

01:40:52.068 --> 01:40:55.704
Come and quench this thirsting of my soul.

01:40:55.704 --> 01:41:00.432
Bread of heaven, feed me till I want no more.

01:41:00.432 --> 01:41:05.159
Fill my cup, fill it up and make me whole.

01:41:05.159 --> 01:41:08.432
I see lights coming on in Cuba.

01:41:08.432 --> 01:41:12.389
It's not the whole island, but Havana mainly.

01:41:12.389 --> 01:41:17.528
Bread of Heaven, feed me till I want no more.

01:41:17.528 --> 01:41:22.667
Fill my cup, fill it up and make me whole.

01:41:22.667 --> 01:41:24.643
Fill my cup, Lord.

01:41:24.643 --> 01:41:26.620
Lift it up, Lord.

01:41:26.620 --> 01:41:30.573
Come and quench this thirsting of my soul.

01:41:30.573 --> 01:41:35.749
Bread of heaven, feed me till I want no more.

01:41:35.749 --> 01:41:40.618
Fill my cup, fill it up and make me whole.

01:41:40.618 --> 01:41:45.486
I don't move until I start to feel that cloak.

01:41:45.486 --> 01:41:57.095
Unless I feel it on me before I start the broadcast, the only way I know to get it to come on is by worship.

01:41:57.095 --> 01:42:07.195
When you give Him praise and worship, that cloak, as I call it, is something I feel come on me and feel when it lifts off.

01:42:07.195 --> 01:42:10.231
It's like a garment that comes on me.

01:42:10.231 --> 01:42:12.357
Whenever it happens, I see.

01:42:27.780 --> 01:42:28.137
But until I feel the breakthrough when it comes on, I can start to see.

01:42:28.137 --> 01:42:30.993
It's just like touching a stove.

01:42:33.135 --> 01:42:35.991
I can't do it without Him; I'm totally helpless without Him.

01:42:35.991 --> 01:42:42.773
Even when I sit on the couch, when that cloak comes on, I feel it.

01:42:42.773 --> 01:42:48.127
When I'm sitting there after the broadcast, I can feel it lift.

01:42:59.026 --> 01:42:59.408
But until then, I can see just sitting on the couch.

01:42:59.408 --> 01:43:04.753
There's levels of it: ankle-deep, knee-deep, waist-deep, and over the head.

01:43:10.481 --> 01:43:10.862
You can feel when it's just ankle-deep.

01:43:10.862 --> 01:43:15.238
It's not too deep; I'm shallow in this tonight.

01:43:15.631 --> 01:43:19.570
I can feel it, but I can still see.

01:43:19.570 --> 01:43:31.385
And then there's some nights like I can feel it coming on me tonight, that it feels like it's going to take me over.

01:43:34.536 --> 01:43:37.816
I don't know how to describe it, but it's so real to me.

01:43:37.816 --> 01:43:49.520
Whenever the anointing comes on so strongly, it's like you get in that river and you taste and see that the Lord is good.

01:44:05.126 --> 01:44:05.466
I acknowledge it when it's like this, especially when I start seeing.

01:44:13.962 --> 01:44:14.302
I can feel it go full.

01:44:14.302 --> 01:44:21.308
Diana knows; she can tell when it comes on in the car when we're driving around.

01:44:37.917 --> 01:44:38.366
I see the whole time; I'm driving down the street, but I'm looking into the spirit as I'm driving.

01:44:43.304 --> 01:44:43.753
It's pretty amazing, but it's all Him.

01:44:43.753 --> 01:44:58.944
That's why I'm trying to teach you to the best of my ability that He's more real than even she is.

01:44:58.944 --> 01:45:00.319
He wants to be real to you.

01:45:09.941 --> 01:45:10.285
To be a forerunner, there's something that's never been done before—to be a pioneer of something.

01:45:20.595 --> 01:45:20.939
When the Lord tells you to go on YouTube and do this, it's gotten increasingly more intense, especially the more I get persecuted.

01:45:20.939 --> 01:45:30.493
I'm so thankful for the opportunity to be able to stand for Him and do the things we've done.

01:45:30.493 --> 01:45:36.951
As I was looking over again, I could see immediately Cuba, and we'll pray into it.

01:45:36.951 --> 01:45:39.946
But the Lord said, 'Stop and explain this.

01:45:39.946 --> 01:45:45.637
' I don't know why; it's for somebody on the other side of this camera.

01:45:45.637 --> 01:45:49.531
Bread of Heaven, feed me till I want no more.

01:45:49.531 --> 01:45:53.582
Fill my cup, fill it up and make me whole.

01:45:53.582 --> 01:45:55.229
Fill my cup, Lord.

01:45:55.229 --> 01:45:56.877
Lift it up, Lord.

01:46:00.172 --> 01:46:00.501
Come and quench this thirsting of my soul.

01:46:00.501 --> 01:46:04.785
Bread of heaven, feed me till I want no more.

01:46:04.785 --> 01:46:09.069
Fill my cup, fill it up and make me whole.

01:46:09.069 --> 01:46:10.716
I see a chicken.

01:46:10.716 --> 01:46:15.329
I see a chicken that looks like it's metal; it's robotic.

01:46:15.329 --> 01:46:19.143
It looks like a ratchet—a ratchet that attaches.

01:46:19.143 --> 01:46:24.951
The chicken has a face and I see designs on this ratchet.

01:46:24.951 --> 01:46:28.435
There's a chicken head with a beak.

01:46:30.758 --> 01:46:32.694
I can see this, but it's being getting wrapped.

01:46:39.663 --> 01:46:40.050
You use the ratchet to tighten the bolts and the screws.

01:46:48.954 --> 01:46:49.342
This chicken moves its head like that, and there's a sun behind it.

01:46:49.342 --> 01:46:55.521
Now, I don't know what that's about yet, but that's what I see.

01:46:55.521 --> 01:46:59.650
It sounds really odd, but it's actually a tool.

01:46:59.650 --> 01:47:10.913
As you move this ratchet—the fat end down here where the ratchet head is—up here, there's a chicken face with a red red thing.

01:47:12.414 --> 01:47:13.541
Help me pull that out.

01:47:13.541 --> 01:47:17.352
What is the Lord trying to say?

01:47:17.352 --> 01:47:21.333
There's a sun behind this ratchet.

01:47:28.780 --> 01:47:29.270
You might say, 'Well, Brandon, that sounds really out there.

01:47:29.270 --> 01:47:32.704
' Well, yeah, it does.

01:47:32.704 --> 01:47:43.006
But there are designs that look like olive leaves; they're all inside.

01:47:43.006 --> 01:47:46.931
I'm looking at it right now.

01:47:46.931 --> 01:47:50.804
I can see the olive leaves.

01:47:50.804 --> 01:48:02.336
It looks like vines, and all these leaves are on the vines on the ratchet that has the chicken head.

01:48:02.336 --> 01:48:11.562
On the face of this ratchet—it's a long one, not round—it's a ratchet with a handle.

01:48:11.562 --> 01:48:18.865
All these olive leaves are all over this ratchet with vines and decorations.

01:48:21.343 --> 01:48:31.256
It looks like paisley almost, but it's carved out with shiny silver with black engravings that look like script all on this ratchet head.

01:48:31.256 --> 01:48:32.908
It's a tool.

01:48:44.126 --> 01:48:44.492
What is a tool?

01:48:54.363 --> 01:48:54.728
It's a wake-up.

01:48:54.728 --> 01:48:57.288
What does a rooster do?

01:48:58.019 --> 01:48:59.116
It wakes everybody up.

01:49:11.347 --> 01:49:11.805
The sun is coming; it's a waking up because the sun is coming.

01:49:13.637 --> 01:49:18.216
The rooster is there on this ratchet, and it's a tool.

01:49:26.001 --> 01:49:26.459
It's a vine, and the vine is attached.

01:49:49.318 --> 01:49:49.949
Is that what the scripture says?

01:49:49.949 --> 01:49:56.262
He is the vine; we are the branches.

01:49:56.262 --> 01:50:12.039
These vines look like olive leaves; they're coming off of this, and all of it is on this tool with the rooster and the sun coming up behind it.

01:50:12.039 --> 01:50:16.347
It looks like the Kellogg's Corn Flakes rooster.

01:50:16.347 --> 01:50:25.395
He uses the rooster to wake you up, to tell you the dawning of a new day.

01:50:25.395 --> 01:50:37.765
Every barnyard animal has its place; every rooster has its place to warn the farmer of a new day.

01:50:37.765 --> 01:50:39.310
They're tools.

01:50:47.546 --> 01:50:48.060
It's a tool, part of the farm.

01:50:48.060 --> 01:50:49.090
Harvesters!

01:50:54.752 --> 01:50:55.267
I hear 'harvesters.

01:50:55.267 --> 01:50:59.892
' Now I see a combine and a silo.

01:50:59.892 --> 01:51:01.654
I see the farmer.

01:51:01.654 --> 01:51:07.643
He has overalls on; I see the hat and the silos in the background.

01:51:07.643 --> 01:51:11.518
I see the rooster that looks like a tool.

01:51:11.518 --> 01:51:16.451
Everything is a tool being used to wake up the farmer.

01:51:16.451 --> 01:51:19.269
It's time to wake up, farmer!

01:51:19.269 --> 01:51:21.888
It's time to wake up, harvesters!

01:51:26.630 --> 01:51:26.909
The silo is empty.

01:51:34.162 --> 01:51:34.441
The Lord said, 'Bring in my harvest.

01:51:34.441 --> 01:51:37.510
' I hear Him say, 'Bring in my harvest.

01:51:50.826 --> 01:51:51.332
The silos are empty; I want them to be overflowing.

01:51:51.332 --> 01:51:59.249
' Now I see the wheat, and the wheat is upon the fields.

01:52:04.745 --> 01:52:05.203
The wheat is bowing down, and the rooster is crowing.

01:52:08.600 --> 01:52:10.160
The sun is coming up for harvest time.

01:52:10.160 --> 01:52:12.241
It's harvest time.

01:52:30.090 --> 01:52:30.419
I see the farmer, and he has buckets in his hands and is running about doing chores and paths throughout the farm, getting ready to bring in this harvest upon the land.

01:52:30.419 --> 01:52:36.012
The Lord shows me these silos; they are massive round silos with dome tops.

01:52:36.012 --> 01:52:45.995
Two of them are red with stripes of white, but there's just a little bit of grain in the bottom of each one.

01:52:45.995 --> 01:52:50.248
The Lord said, 'Bring in my harvest, son.

01:52:50.248 --> 01:52:58.753
' I don't know about you, but there is a key to understanding and an intricate...

01:52:58.753 --> 01:53:04.281
the elderly man that's walking around has a big nose.

01:53:04.281 --> 01:53:19.026
He has brown hair that's cut well, and he has a straw hat on with a straw out of his mouth.

01:53:19.026 --> 01:53:23.692
He's wearing a plaid shirt.

01:53:23.692 --> 01:53:32.394
His shirt is plaid, short-sleeved; it looks like a linen shirt.

01:53:32.394 --> 01:53:44.928
He has overalls and the two buckets in his hands, and he's running to go do something.

01:53:45.524 --> 01:53:50.896
I can see him; I see the farmhouse.

01:54:01.042 --> 01:54:01.639
I see that strange-looking rooster with the metal body.

01:54:06.125 --> 01:54:09.273
Now I see a dog, and I see the dog that is the farmer's dog.

01:54:09.273 --> 01:54:15.219
This dog is brown with black spots and a really pink tongue, looking around.

01:54:15.219 --> 01:54:21.166
It's looking toward the farmer as he's running with those buckets in his hands.

01:54:25.364 --> 01:54:25.713
The dog is at a full sprint.

01:54:47.371 --> 01:54:47.776
He is on a path.

01:54:50.617 --> 01:54:53.458
It looks like a dirt path that goes into some corn.

01:55:03.198 --> 01:55:03.604
The Lord has such a sense of humor.

01:55:03.604 --> 01:55:08.879
Everything is in color, and it looks like a cartoon.

01:55:12.909 --> 01:55:13.300
The grass is green, but that harvest is plentiful.

01:55:13.300 --> 01:55:18.386
There is only one harvester: this man and his buckets.

